text: Sanjeet Desai (born 12 December 1997) is an Indian cricketer. He made his List A debut for Chhattisgarh in the 2017–18 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 12 February 2018. He made his first-class debut for Chhattisgarh in the 2018–19 Ranji Trophy on 1 November 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Chhattisgarh cricketers
